{"tid":365331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 S1 唔見銀包","createTime":"2017-08-19T06:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T14:01:07.000Z","uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e586f057848fab9bfc49004fb0a7c017c9984924","tid":365331,"uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱趕返工搭巴士S1跌左個紫紅色皮嘅散銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神通廣大嘅連登大神幫幫手<br />\n如果有好心人執到就聯絡我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排不斷跌野已經俾老母屌到上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我坐下層最後排最右毒撚位<br />\n內有學生八達通同幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一日人工黎<br />\n<br />\n冇錢食飯返屋企了<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家"},{"pid":"e4112a73582b84b8348216af66e7ccd5746b4924","tid":365331,"uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533de3697fce01b7c7f85b7581a53451c1c4340d","tid":365331,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4443c2852849341be2bc5f0c6958e8d6591b4efc","tid":365331,"uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118df829899c6e25d4cf67d9922b7be1fa484d2f","tid":365331,"uid":138013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d05f2fe3c81f236a2d3e532a6d0c80bc0bd78f55","tid":365331,"uid":75519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited